name: Pectantis Mococo
description:
--Fig05--
Pectantis Mococo is a Calceara Crustacean creature from Yanyan, an exoplanet located 2011 light years away from Earth, orbiting the star Bubup.
Pectantis fruits have one of the best flavors nature has ever produced through the universe, besides that one of them is capable of giving all nutrients an animal needs for a whole year in Yanyan.
The species grows its own fruits and feeds on them, having to protect it at all costs, so it developed two claw-like structures to keep its food safe.
Fruits also compose its reproductive system, just like trees, so intentionally it lets some of the fruits drop and be carried away by the wind and storms to create new individuals.
